STEWART
v.
MOORE FAMILY CARE, et al. No. 335P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 5, 2015. Robert K. Stewart, Marion, for Stewart, Robert K. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 2nd of October 2015 by Plaintiff for Medical Malpractice Civil Action:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of November 2015."
